data.description: A Beautiful Setting in Historic Sautee Nacoochee GA. Sitting on 3.09 walkable and inviting acres. This 3BR/3BA one level home is full of charm and creativity. The primary suite is spacious with upgraded finishes including a elegant private bath & walk-in closet. The open great room is light and bright with a fireplace and vaulted ceilings. The sunroom and covered porch extends the gracious living area, bringing the outdoors inside. Outside, there is a handy workshop in the unfinished basement plus a large 2 Car Garage that attaches to the home with a nice breezeway extending the inviting front porch space. Sautee Woods Trail is a paved county maintained road. $100 a year HOA Fees. This is an Estate Sale. (Septic system is for a 2BR home.)
